1 Individual requiring treatment - Assistance - Medical care.
2 A peace officer, as defined under section 12 - 63 - 01, may transport an individual to a loca l
3 hospital, detoxification center, community behavioral health center, or other appropriate
4 treatment facility. A tier 1b mental health professional, as defined under section 25 - 01 - 01, of a
